ng-content

ng g c ngcontent

ng g c ngtemplate

ng g c input-binding

ng g c input-binding/child

ng g c ciclovida


Tipos de Pipe

https://angular.io/api?type=pipe


ng g c exemploPipe

Criando um pipe
---------------

ng g p capitalize


Rotas
-----

Gerando m?dulo de rotas
-----------------------

ng generate module app-routing --flat --module=app

de: import { CommonModule } from '@angular/common';
para: import { RouterModule, Routes } from '@angular/router';


Formul?rios
-----------

Criar template form
-------------------

ng g c template-form

Componente para debug de formul?rio
-----------------------------------

ng g c form-debug


-----------------------------------------------------------


BackEnd fake usando Json-server
-------------------------------

Install JSON Server

npm install -g json-server

Start JSON Server

json-server --watch db.json

